02:38.323 --> 02:42.058
♪ Sometimes it feels like
things are outta control ♪

02:42.093 --> 02:45.328
♪ Like you're living in a circus ♪

02:45.363 --> 02:49.232
♪ Tryin' to figure out
your way in the world ♪

02:49.267 --> 02:52.135
♪ Where you're at is kinda perfect ♪

02:52.170 --> 02:54.170
♪ So turn it up, turn it up ♪

02:54.206 --> 02:56.072
♪ Do your thing, don't stop ♪

02:56.107 --> 02:59.108
♪ Let the games begin,
let's jump right in ♪

