Guys, I promise you,
we weren't hiding anything.

03:29.074 --> 03:30.406
This is news to us, too.

03:30.442 --> 03:32.141
We never really looked
at the birth certificates,

03:32.177 --> 03:33.376
which frankly,
I'm impressed we still have.

03:33.411 --> 03:35.411
And to be fair, it was eight hours

03:35.447 --> 03:39.082
of horrible pain, followed by
eight years of craziness.

03:39.117 --> 03:40.383
What were you guys
doing in the attic anyway?

03:40.418 --> 03:42.285
You know it's off limits.

03:42.320 --> 03:45.088
I'm sorry, but this place
is drowning in Diazes.

03:45.123 --> 03:46.356
I needed some air.

03:46.391 --> 03:49.092
Besides, we were only
up there the one time.

03:49.127 --> 03:52.161
Not a lie. I've been up there a bunch,

03:52.197 --> 03:54.430
but we've only been up there one time.

03:54.466 --> 03:57.333
Let's not give them too long
to think about this.

03:57.369 --> 03:59.335
Lewie, Beast, different birthdays.

03:59.371 --> 04:02.338
Let's move on to a more
exciting topic, like groceries.

04:02.374 --> 04:05.141
Who wants to finish
unloading the car? I do!

04:05.176 --> 04:08.311
For our whole lives, we've had
our party on my birthday.

04:08.346 --> 04:10.346
That doesn't seem fair to Beast.

04:10.382 --> 04:12.148
Thanks, almost twin.

04:12.183 --> 04:15.385
Okay, this year, when you turn nine,

04:15.420 --> 04:17.487
you'll each get your own party.

04:17.522 --> 04:19.289
And there goes the only benefit

04:19.324 --> 04:21.089
of having two kids at once.

04:21.125 --> 04:23.159
We'll do Lewie's party on the 20th,

04:23.194 --> 04:24.360
and Beast's on the 21st.

04:24.396 --> 04:26.195
Yes, got the dates right!

04:26.231 --> 04:28.364
We're really sorry, guys.
We can't change the past,

04:28.400 --> 04:30.333
but we can fix it in the future.

04:30.368 --> 04:32.335
And since your birthday's
not for a while,

04:32.370 --> 04:34.370
take this as an early present.

04:34.406 --> 04:37.140
We know you're buying our love.

04:37.175 --> 04:38.274
And it's working.

04:39.411 --> 04:41.177
Yes!

04:41.212 --> 04:43.212
That was close.

04:43.248 --> 04:45.214
Just another example of
why whipped cream

04:45.250 --> 04:47.350
is one of nature's super foods.

04:47.385 --> 04:49.485
Now, if you'll excuse me.

